## Typography

**Sans:** `Plus Jakarta Sans` — all body text, labels, buttons, headings
**Mono:** `JetBrains Mono` — verb levels, file types, gate codes, phase indices, percentages, any metric

Rule: **sans carries voice; mono carries metric.**

```css
--font-sans: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
--font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
```

Global base: `letter-spacing: -0.01em` on body. Never use Inter, Roboto, or system fonts as primary.

---

## Components

All component patterns are defined as `.tp-*` classes in `/refs/styles.css`. When building in React/Tailwind, replicate the same visual output — use the CSS classes directly via CSS Modules, or translate to Tailwind utilities that match exactly.

### Buttons

```
.tp-btn-primary  → accent bg (#DBFD6B), ink text, pill shape (border-radius: 999px), lime glow shadow
.tp-btn-ghost    → transparent bg, border: --border-strong
.tp-btn-sm       → smaller padding variant
.tp-btn-pos      → green bg, white text
.tp-btn-neg      → red bg, white text
```

Hover on primary: `translateY(-1px)` + shadow lift. Transition: `0.12s`.

### Ghost / Add Buttons

Dashed border (`1.5px dashed rgba(219,253,107,0.55)`), transparent bg. On hover: `--accent-soft` bg, solid accent border, ink text. Used for "＋ Add Phase", "＋ Add Block" inline actions.

### Cards

White surface, `--radius-lg`, `--shadow-sm`, `--border`. Active cards get `border-left: 3px solid var(--accent)` and `--shadow-md`.

### Pills & Tags

```
.tp-pill      → accent-soft bg, rounded, 11px sans, 600 weight
.tp-pill-mono → mono font, uppercase, 0.06em letter-spacing
.tp-tag-dev   → accent-soft bg (Development)
.tp-tag-test  → pos-soft bg, pos color (Testing)
.tp-tag-anal  → blue-soft bg, blue color (Analysis & Design)
.tp-tag-trans → muted-soft bg (Transversal)
```

### Status Badges

Dot indicator (`::before`, 6px circle, currentColor) + label. Three states:
- `pending` → muted bg, ink-2 text
- `passed` → pos-soft bg, pos text
- `failed` → neg-soft bg, neg text

### Progress Bar

6px height, `rgba(28,31,51,0.06)` track, `linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), #c9ed5a)` fill. Always border-radius 999px.

### Gate Marker

Dashed border container, semi-transparent bg gradient. Left icon: 40px circle. States: default (ink border), passed (pos border + pos-soft bg), failed (neg border + neg-soft bg).

### Top Bar

`background: rgba(255,255,255,0.55)`, `backdrop-filter: blur(8px)`, bottom border `--border`. Logo mark: 26px square, `border-radius: 7px`, ink bg, accent text, mono font.

---

## Page Structure Rules

- Topbar is always fixed/sticky, frosted glass
- Page content uses `overflow-y: auto` with hidden scrollbars (`::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none }`)
- Vertical timeline layout: phases stack top-to-bottom, blocks nested inside phases, gates auto-generated between blocks
- All interactive additions (phases, blocks) use ghost dashed buttons — never a traditional form input exposed raw
- Modals: centered, `--radius-lg`, `--shadow-lg`, surface bg, backdrop blur overlay

---

## Do / Don't

| ✅ Do | ❌ Don't |
|---|---|
| Use `var(--accent)` for all primary actions | Hardcode `#DBFD6B` outside `:root` |
| Use JetBrains Mono for all numeric metrics | Use sans for percentages or gate codes |
| Use `tp-*` class patterns as reference | Use default shadcn styles without restyling |
| Apply page gradient on every page wrapper | Use flat `bg-gray-100` or similar |
| Use dashed ghost buttons for add actions | Use icon-only buttons without label for add |
| Keep transitions at 0.12s–0.2s | Use slow 0.5s+ transitions |

